com.github.moribund.net.packets.key

Class KeyUnpressedPacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.moribund.net.packets.key.KeyUnpressedPacket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OutgoingPacket

    public class KeyUnpressedPacket
extends java.lang.Object
implements OutgoingPacket
    Sends a packet to the server as soon as a key is released. Key sending is synchronous, meaning that it is sent to the server as soon as it happens, not in accordance to the 100 MS game state.
